<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000117> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "b has occurrent part c =Def c occurrent part of b"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000117> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Mary's life has occurrent part Mary's 5th birthday"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000117> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "has occurrent part"@en .
