<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "8/17/09: specified inputs of one process are not necessarily specified inputs of a larger process that it is part of. This is in contrast to how 'has participant' works." .
