<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000179> "p-boundary" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000180> "ProcessBoundary" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "the boundary between the 2nd and 3rd year of your life."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "p is a process boundary =Def. p is a temporal part of a process & p has no proper temporal parts. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [084-001])"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000601> "Every process boundary occupies_temporal_region a zero-dimensional temporal region. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [085-002])"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000602> "(forall (x) (if (ProcessBoundary x) (exists (y) (and (ZeroDimensionalTemporalRegion y) (occupiesTemporalRegion x y))))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [085-002] " .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000602> "(iff (ProcessBoundary a) (exists (p) (and (Process p) (temporalPartOf a p) (not (exists (b) (properTemporalPartOf b a)))))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [084-001] " .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "084-BFO" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo.owl> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "process boundary"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "p is a process boundary =Def p is a temporal part of a process & p has no proper temporal parts"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "The boundary between the 2nd and 3rd year of your life"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000035> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "process boundary"@en .
