# https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000197
<https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000197> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
