<https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000482> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Überschriften, Kapitel, Themenfelder, Kompetenzbereiche"@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000493
<https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000493> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000493> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/lehrplan/ontology/LP_0000478> .
