<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000120> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Class has all its metadata, but is either not guaranteed to be in its final location in the asserted IS_A hierarchy or refers to another class that is not complete."@en .
